The most crucial condition for the success of the SDR and DSP processes in efficient spin generation is τsc > τs > τnr. Here, a much longer spin lifetime of the defect electron, denoted by τsc, ensures that the Gai2+\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
